The Kanetik Billing Library is a substantial rewrite of MakeBillingEasy,
upgraded to Google Play Billing Library 8.x with a typed exception
hierarchy, lifecycle-aware connection sharing, exponential backoff retry
logic, hardened error mapping, and a pluggable logger interface. The
original MakeBillingEasy attribution is preserved here per
Apache License 2.0 §4.
